                <p>In the future we will improve Hackevents to offer you an even better service.</p>
                <p>Hackathons by region: <a href="/hackathon/germany">Germany</a> - <a href="/hackathon/usa">United States</a> - <a href="/hackathons/europe">Europe</a> - <a href="/hackathons">Worldwide</a></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- end:upcoming featured -->

          <!-- begin: Click to Action -->
          <div id="subscribe">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-12">
                  <h3>Sign up now and personalize your hackathon search
                    <br>
                    <small>Hackevents built a hackathon recomenndation engine to provide you with even better and more relevant events</small>
                  </h3>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-xs-12">
                  <% unless current_user %>
                    <a href"#" class="btn btn-default btn-lg col-xs-6">Find out more</a>
                    <%= link_to "Join the community", '/auth/twitter', method: 'get', class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg col-xs-6" %>
